thread.title: Diane Cahill
thread.title_full: Extra Space Storage reviewed by Diane Cahill

author: Diane Cahill
title: Diane Cahill
text: My experience with Extra Space Storage on J. Clyde Morris Blvd. has been wonderful! The facility is so clean and safe and the location is great with easy access to I-64. The staff, Teddy and David, are phenomenal! They are both so professional, caring, and offer many great tips on packing and moving. I highly recommend them and Extra Space Storage to every one. Thank you so much for all you do!
